=======================HROTHGAR PARALLEL MINIMIZER=======================

Copyright (C) 2007-2012 Andisheh Mahdavi. Copying and distribution of
this README, with or without modification, are permitted in any medium
without royalty provided the copyright notice and this notice are
preserved.

This package contains Hrothgar, a generic Levenberg-Marquardt
minimizer and Markov Chain Monte Carlo generator that is well suited
to complicated multidimensional problems.  The contact is
Andisheh Mahdavi (andisheh.mahdavi@gmail.com).

For specific installation instructions see hrothgar.pdf. For general
instruction for using the GNU auto tools, please read the INSTALL file
included in this distribution.

